'''R. A. Salvatore''' (born [[January 20]], [[1950s#1959|1959]]) is an author of two ''[[Star Wars]]'' and many fantasy novels, most famous for his works related to the ''Forgotten Realms'' setting for ''Dungeons and Dragons''. He also came up with the idea for the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]'s strict use of biotechnology.

